The paper deals with the application of Gaussian process regression in safe control of robotic systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
